sources.title: I Am Omega | Full Action Adventure Movie
sources.description:
I Am Omega - In post apocalyptic LA being rampaged by zombie like cannibals humans that have some kind of genetic infection.  Local man Renchard is forced to live a daily struggle as he tries to locate radio signals and find a cure.
2007.  Stars: Mark Dacascos, Geoff Meed, Jennifer Lee Wiggins
